  "helpArticleAccount": "Common account issues and solutions:\n\n• Forgot Password: Use the \"Forgot Password\" link on the login screen\n• Account Verification: Check your email for verification links\n• Profile Updates: Go to Profile > Edit Profile to update your information\n• Account Security: Enable two-factor authentication in Privacy & Security settings\n• Data Privacy: Review your privacy settings in the app settings",
  "helpArticlePayment": "Payment and billing assistance:\n\n• Payment Methods: Add credit cards, mobile money, or bank accounts\n• Refund Requests: Contact support for booking cancellations and refunds\n• Payment History: View all transactions in your profile\n• Failed Payments: Check your payment method and try again\n• Currency: All payments are processed in Rwandan Francs (RWF)",
  "helpArticleBooking": "Event booking and management:\n\n• Booking Events: Browse events and tap \"Book Now\" to reserve your spot\n• Booking Confirmation: You'll receive email and app notifications\n• Cancel Bookings: Go to My Bookings to cancel upcoming events\n• Event Updates: Check the Events tab for latest information\n• Group Bookings: Contact support for group reservations",
  "helpArticlePlaces": "Places and location information:\n\n• Finding Places: Use the search bar or browse categories\n• Place Details: Tap on any place to see photos, reviews, and information\n• Directions: Get directions using your preferred maps app\n• Reviews: Share your experiences by writing reviews\n• Favorites: Save places you want to visit later",
  "helpFaqGs1Q": "How do I create an account?",
  "helpFaqGs1A": "Download the app and tap \"Sign Up\" to create your account with email or phone number.",
  "helpFaqGs2Q": "How do I book my first event?",
  "helpFaqGs2A": "Browse events in the Events tab, select an event, and tap \"Book Now\" to reserve your spot.",
  "helpFaqGs3Q": "How do I update my profile?",
  "helpFaqGs3A": "Go to Profile > Edit Profile to update your personal information.",
  "helpFaqGs4Q": "How do I find places to visit?",
  "helpFaqGs4A": "Use the Explore tab to discover places, or search for specific locations.",
  "helpFaqGs5Q": "How do I get help?",
  "helpFaqGs5A": "Use this Help Center, contact support, or check our FAQ section.",
  "helpFaqAc1Q": "How do I change my password?",
  "helpFaqAc1A": "Go to Profile > Privacy & Security > Change Password to update your password.",
  "helpFaqAc2Q": "How do I update my email?",
  "helpFaqAc2A": "Go to Profile > Edit Profile to update your email address.",
  "helpFaqAc3Q": "How do I delete my account?",
  "helpFaqAc3A": "Contact support to request account deletion. This action cannot be undone.",
  "helpFaqAc4Q": "How do I enable two-factor authentication?",
  "helpFaqAc4A": "Go to Profile > Privacy & Security to enable 2FA for added security.",
  "helpFaqAc5Q": "How do I update my profile picture?",
  "helpFaqAc5A": "Go to Profile > Edit Profile and tap on your profile picture to change it.",
  "helpFaqAc6Q": "How do I change my phone number?",
  "helpFaqAc6A": "Go to Profile > Edit Profile to update your phone number.",
  "helpFaqAc7Q": "How do I verify my account?",
  "helpFaqAc7A": "Check your email for verification links and follow the instructions.",
  "helpFaqAc8Q": "How do I download my data?",
  "helpFaqAc8A": "Go to Profile > Privacy & Security > Download Data to request your data.",
  "helpFaqBk1Q": "How do I book an event?",
  "helpFaqBk1A": "Browse events, select one, and tap \"Book Now\" to complete your booking.",
  "helpFaqBk2Q": "How do I cancel a booking?",
  "helpFaqBk2A": "Go to My Bookings, find your booking, and tap \"Cancel Booking\".",
  "helpFaqBk3Q": "How do I get my event tickets?",
  "helpFaqBk3A": "Your tickets will be sent via email and available in the app.",
  "helpFaqBk4Q": "Can I book for multiple people?",
  "helpFaqBk4A": "Yes, select the number of people when booking an event.",
  "helpFaqBk5Q": "How do I get a refund?",
  "helpFaqBk5A": "Contact support for refund requests. Refund policy varies by event.",
  "helpFaqBk6Q": "How do I reschedule a booking?",
  "helpFaqBk6A": "Cancel your current booking and book a new time slot.",
  "helpFaqBk7Q": "How do I check my booking status?",
  "helpFaqBk7A": "Go to My Bookings to see all your reservations and their status.",
  "helpFaqBk8Q": "What if an event is cancelled?",
  "helpFaqBk8A": "You'll be notified and can request a full refund or transfer to another event.",
  "helpFaqBk9Q": "How do I book a hotel?",
  "helpFaqBk9A": "Browse hotels in the Explore tab and follow the booking process.",
  "helpFaqBk10Q": "How do I book a tour?",
  "helpFaqBk10A": "Find tours in the Explore tab and book them like events.",
  "helpFaqBk11Q": "How do I get directions to an event?",
  "helpFaqBk11A": "Tap on the event location to open it in your maps app.",
  "helpFaqBk12Q": "How do I share an event?",
  "helpFaqBk12A": "Tap the share button on any event to share it with friends.",
  "helpFaqPy1Q": "What payment methods are accepted?",
  "helpFaqPy1A": "We accept credit cards, mobile money, and bank transfers.",
  "helpFaqPy2Q": "How do I add a payment method?",
  "helpFaqPy2A": "Go to Profile > Payment Methods to add your preferred payment option.",
  "helpFaqPy3Q": "How do I get a refund?",
  "helpFaqPy3A": "Contact support with your booking details to request a refund.",
  "helpFaqPy4Q": "How long do refunds take?",
  "helpFaqPy4A": "Refunds typically take 3-5 business days to process.",
  "helpFaqPy5Q": "Is my payment information secure?",
  "helpFaqPy5A": "Yes, we use industry-standard encryption to protect your data.",
  "helpFaqPy6Q": "How do I update my payment method?",
  "helpFaqPy6A": "Go to Profile > Payment Methods to update your payment information.",
  "helpFaqTx1Q": "The app is not loading properly",
  "helpFaqTx1A": "Try closing and reopening the app, or restart your device.",
  "helpFaqTx2Q": "I can't log in to my account",
  "helpFaqTx2A": "Check your internet connection and verify your login credentials.",
  "helpFaqTx3Q": "The app crashes frequently",
  "helpFaqTx3A": "Update to the latest version of the app from your app store.",
  "helpFaqTx4Q": "I'm not receiving notifications",
  "helpFaqTx4A": "Check your notification settings in your device settings and app settings.",
